WEBVTT

00:15:58.274 --> 00:16:01.468
and you're not going to be perfect
as predicting the future.

00:16:01.492 --> 00:16:03.708
AG: So they started doing
some market research.

00:16:03.732 --> 00:16:05.108
BA: We used to have a saying

00:16:05.132 --> 00:16:07.730
that you listen to anecdotes
and you act on data.

00:16:07.754 --> 00:16:09.886
AG: After figuring out
there was real demand,

00:16:09.910 --> 00:16:12.672
they decided to develop pants
that could fit the super-fit.

00:16:12.696 --> 00:16:15.407
BA: And thus the athletic-fit
pant was born.

00:16:15.431 --> 00:16:17.420
AG: And it's become super popular.

00:16:17.444 --> 00:16:19.869
Tyler remembers
the first time he sold a pair.

00:16:19.893 --> 00:16:23.075
TK: His heart, I think, exploded
but he didn't cry.

00:16:23.099 --> 00:16:25.285
It was right then we knew --

00:16:25.309 --> 00:16:27.239
oh my gosh, we've got something here.

00:16:27.787 --> 00:16:30.532
AG: Bonobos makes great clothes
that can fit every guy.